items.title: Generative Artificial Intelligence (AI) in Digital Marketing Market Opportunities and Strategies Report 2025-2034: Top 10 Players Control Just 15.2%, with IBM Leading at 3.48% Share
items.description: The global generative AI in digital marketing market will surge from $2.48 billion in 2024 to $35.12 billion in 2034, driven by demand for personalization and AI advancements. North America leads with a 33.66% share. Key growth sectors include mobile marketing and content generation. Major players like IBM and Google dominate, with evolving strategies focusing on AI-powered advertising and video tools.
